0Supriya%20Sule%20told%20NDTV%20today.%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20daughter%20of%20veteran%20politician%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20is%20set%20to%20contest%20again%20from%20the%20Baramati%20parliamentary%20constituency%20that%20she%20has%20represented%20since%202009.%20A%20family%20stronghold%2C%20the%20seat%20was%20earlier%20represented%20by%20Mr%20Pawar%20from%201996%20to%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%2C%20however%2C%20is%20different.%20Between%20the%20last%20election%20and%20this%20one%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20has%20split%20-%20one%20faction%20is%20led%20by%20the%20octogenarian%20and%20the%20other%20by%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20has%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20joined%20the%20Maharashtra%20government.%20Ms%20Sule%20will%20now%20be%20contesting%20as%20a%20candidate%20of%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%2C%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20the%20veteran.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20battle%20for%20Baramati%20this%20time%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20may%20see%20a%20Pawar%20vs%20Pawar%20contest.%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20and%20environmental%20activist%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20on%20her%20sister-in-law%20Supriya%20on%20the%20key%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20this%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20who%20is%20contesting%20against%20me%20because%20it%20has%20not%20been%20announced%20officially.%20I%20will%20tell%20you%20once%20that%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20poll%20prospects%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20and%20split%20in%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDemocracy%20is%20being%20murdered.%20The%20ones%20who%20went%20to%20BJP%20did%20not%20do%20so%20out%20of%20love.%20They%20went%20because%20of%20ICE%20-%20Income%20tax%20(department)%2C%20CBI%20and%20ED.%20The%20BJP%20had%20raised%20a%20storm%20over%20Ashok%20Chavan.%20And%20now%20they%20have%20taken%20him%20in.%20This%20is%20how%20they%20are%20breaking%20parties.%20This%20is%20not%20politics%2C%20this%20is%20murder%20of%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%2C%20a%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20was%20formed%20to%20resign%20over%20allegations%20of%20corruption%2C%20quit%20the%20Congress%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20she%20is%20confident%20of%20another%20victory%20in%20Baramati%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20work%20is%20in%20front%20of%20everyone%2C%20so%20is%20my%20parliamentary%20performance.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20allegation%20of%20corruption%20against%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711267200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm0rtkrsg_supriya-sule_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-baramati-leaders-going-to-bjp-because-of-ice-income-tax-cbi-ed-supriya-sule-5301388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leaders%20from%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20not%20going%20to%20the%20BJP%20because%20they%20like%20its%20ideology%2C%20but%20because%20of%20%26quot%3BICE%20-%20Income%20Tax%2C%20CBI%20and%20ED%26quot%3B%2C%20three-time%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20told%20NDTV%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-baramati-leaders-going-to-bjp-because-of-ice-income-tax-cbi-ed-supriya-sule-5301388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Serbians%20angry%20at%20Trump%20family%20deal%20for%20site%20of%20NATO%20bombing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711267045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108746944%2Cimgsize-24526.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fserbians-angry-at-trump-family-deal-for-site-of-nato-bombing%2