e%20is%20a%20scarcity%20of%20water%20and%20appropriate%20directions%20should%20be%20issued%20to%20the%20officials%20so%20that%20people%20don't%20face%20any%20problem'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20in%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMessage%20From%20Jail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20yesterday%20urged%20everyone%20to%20continue%20working%20for%20the%20society%20and%20not%20hate%20anyone%2C%20even%20those%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20was%20read%20out%20by%20his%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20forces%20within%20and%20outside%20India%20that%20are%20weakening%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20jail%20that%20can%20keep%20him%20behind%20bars%20for%20long.%20I%20will%20come%20out%20soon%20and%20keep%20my%20promises%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20in%20his%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Prison%20Rules%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20law%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%20says%20that%20an%20inmate%20can%20only%20hold%20two%20meetings%20in%20a%20week%2C%20which%20would%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20carry%20out%20his%20responsibilities%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20measure%20that%20could%20facilitate%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20governance%20from%20within%20the%20confinement%20was%20if%20he%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20the%20power%20to%20convert%20any%20building%20into%20a%20prison%2C%20and%20if%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20can%20convince%20him%20to%20put%20him%20under%20house%20arrest%20-%20it%20would%20help%20him%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20day-to-day%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20administrator%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20declare%20any%20building%20as%20a%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gupta%20told%20NDTV.%3