aid%20that%20it%20is%20currently%20analysing%20the%20footage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-metro-responds-after-video-of-girls-playing-holi-on-train-goes-viral-5300832%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20The%20Citigroup%20Unit%20That%20Was%20Plagued%20By%20Harassment%2C%20Drugs%20For%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBankers%20from%20Citigroup%20Inc.%20were%20partying%20with%20clients%20one%20night%20in%20May%202018%20at%20a%20downtown%20Manhattan%20hot%20spot%20called%20Catch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20a%20recent%20college%20grad%2C%20had%20landed%20in%20the%20equities%20division%20for%20her%20two-year%20rotational%20program%20at%20the%20bank%20and%20had%20brought%20her%20roommate%20along%20to%20the%20party.%20As%20the%20evening%20progressed%2C%20one%20of%20the%20unit's%20bosses%20came%20up%20behind%20the%20roommate%20and%20surprised%20her%20by%20grinding%20his%20crotch%20against%20her%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20who%20said%20they%20saw%20him.%20Months%20later%2C%20that%20rotator%20said%2C%20a%20male%20trader%20told%20her%20to%20wear%20shorter%20skirts%20and%20higher%20heels%20to%20work%20and%20made%20multiple%20inquiries%20into%20her%20love%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterviews%20with%2022%20people%20who%20worked%20in%20or%20closely%20with%20the%20equities%20division%20suggest%20the%20incidents%20weren't%20an%20aberration%2C%20painting%20a%20picture%20of%20persistent%20harassment%20and%20discrimination%20at%20Citigroup's%20equities%20unit%20in%20New%20York%2C%20which%20advises%20on%20and%20executes%20trades%20for%20top%20hedge%20funds%20and%20other%20Wall%20Street%20players.%20The%20accounts%20echo%20allegations%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20last%20year%20by%20a%20managing%20director%20who%20claims%20such%20conduct%20continued%20until%20as%20recently%20as%202022.%20After%20the%20lawsuit%20hit%2C%20the%20firm's%20trading%20chief%20reminded%20staff%20to%20speak%20up%20if%20they%20observe%20misconduct%2C%20echoing%20the%20company's%20standard%20conduct%20trainings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20at%20least%20a%20decade%2C%20employees%20openly%20ogled%20female%20colleagues%2C%20rated%20them%20by%20their%20looks%20and%20bragged%20about%20their%20sexual%20conquests%2C%20according%20to%20the%20interviews%20with%20the%20workers%2C%20who%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20because%20of%20concerns%20about%20retaliation.%20Boorish%20behavior%20at%20the%20division%20included%20the%20use%20of%20cocaine%20in%20the%20office%2C%20they%20said.%20Complaints%20to%20senior%20executives%20and%20human%20resources%20didn't%20lead%20to%20change%2C%20fueling%20the%20perception%20of%20an%20insulated%20in-crowd%20and%20prompting%20several%20employees%20to%20leave%20while%20some%20alleged%20perpetrators%20remain%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitigroup%2C%20which%20three%20years%20ago%20made%20history%20by%20appointing%20Jane%20Fraser%20as%20the%20first%20female%20CEO%20of%20a%20major%20US%20bank%2C%20has%20led%20rivals%20on%20many%20measures%20of%20a%20more%20equitable%20culture.%20Yet%20the%20behavior%20within%20the%20stock-trading%20unit%20stood%20out%20even%20in%20an%20industry%20that%20has%20struggled%20for%20decades%20to%20rein%20in%20conduct%20that%20makes%20women%20feel%20unwelcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Citigroup%2C%20Mark%20Costiglio%2C%20said%20no%20one%20should%20be%20discriminated%20against%20or%20harassed%20at%20work.%20%26quot%3BOur%20efforts%20to%20foster%20an%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20workplace%20culture%20never%20stop%2C%20and%20ensuring%20that%20our%20standards%20are%20well%20understood%20and%20complied%20with%20by%20everyone%20at%20Citi%20is%20a%20continuous%2C%20proactive%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20provide%20colleagues%20with%20a%20number%20of%20avenues%20to%20raise%20concerns%20in%20confidence%2C%20and%20when%20substantiated%20we%20will%20take%20appropriate%20action%2C%20up%20to%20and%20including%20termination%20of%20employment.%20While%20we%20will%20not%20comment%20on%20individual%20internal%20matters%2C%20simply%20put%2C%20where%20warranted%2C%20we%20exit%20employees%20who%20fail%20to%20meet%20our%20high%20standards%20of%20respectful%20treatment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20its%20fixed-income%20prowess%2C%20Citigroup%20has%20long%20ranked%20last%20among%20the%20big%20five%20Wall%20Street%20banks%20in%20equities%20trading%20revenue.%20Despite%20efforts%20to%20change%20that%2C%20it's%20fallen%20further%20behind%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20which%20generates%20about%20%245%20billion%20more%20in%20revenue%20from%20the%20business%2C%20a%20gap%20that%20was%20roughly%20%243%20billion%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20investment%20banks%20typically%20have%20a%20little%20more%20than%201%2C000%20front-office%20employees%20in%20their%20equities%20trading%20divisions%2C%20according%20to%20consultancy%20Coalition%20Greenwich.%20Citigroup%20doesn't%20disclose%20its%20team's%20size%2C%20but%20that%20would%20make%20its%20group%20a%20small%2C%20though%20lucrative%2C%20part%20of%20its%20240%2C000-person%20global%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20equities%20division's%20leadership%20was%20rejiggered%20five%20times%20in%20about%2012%20years%2C%20a%20period%20that%20saw%20the%20unit%20grapple%20with%20repeated%20bouts%20of%20misbehavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20female%20derivatives%20trader%20recalled%20sitting%20at%20a%20client%20dinner%20at%20Locanda%20Verde%20near%20the%20bank's%20headquarters%20in%202010%20when%20a%20colleague%20reached%20under%20the%20table%20and%20put%20his%20hand%20on%20her%20leg.%20Around%20that%20time%2C%20she%20said%2C%20a%20research%20analyst%20asked%20her%20why%20she%20didn't%20wear%20sexier%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20HR%20and%20senior%20managers%20about%20both%2C%20describing%20an%20ugly%20culture%20that%20she%20saw%20as%20pervasive%2C%20and%20remembers%20one%20female%20executive%20encouraging%20her%20to%20brush%20it%20off.%20Years%20later%2C%20the%20conversation%20stands%20out%20as%20disheartening.%20One%20colleague%20remembered%20the%20trader%20speaking%20about%20harassment%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20another%20recalled%20hearing%20about%20the%20exchange%20with%20the%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20several%20of%20the%20alleged%20incidents%20would%20clearly%20violate%20Citi's%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20we%20have%20not%20identified%20a%20complaint%20being%20filed%20for%20several%20of%20them%2C%20others%20are%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20old%2C%20and%20some%20contain%20allegations%20that%20are%20either%20baseless%2C%20too%20vague%2C%20or%20involve%20people%20who%20have%20left%20the%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Costiglio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20women%20said%20they%20stayed%20quiet%20about%20being%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20colleagues%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20retaliation%20in%20an%20industry%20that%20prizes%20discretion%20and%20loyalty.%20Six%20people%20there%20besides%20the%20derivatives%20trader%20said%20that%20they%20complained%20about%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20workplace%20misconduct%20to%20senior%20colleagues%20or%20human%20resources%20and%20were%20disappointed%20with%20the%20outcome%2C%20feeling%20the%20bank%20didn't%20take%20sufficient%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20said%20they%20described%20separate%20incidents%20to%20Dan%20Keegan%2C%20who%20ran%20Citigroup's%20trading%20business%20across%20North%20America.%20According%20to%20one%20of%20them%2C%20Keegan%20was%20told%20that%20senior%20staffers%20egged%20on%20a%20junior%20banker%20to%20show%20the%20underwear%20of%20a%20woman%20he'd%20apparently%20slept%20with%3B%20Keegan%2C%20who%20left%20Citigroup%20in%202022%2C%20didn't%20respond%20to%20messages.%20Five%20people%20saw%20the%20incident%20or%20heard%20about%20it%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20young%20banker%20was%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20person%20involved%20in%20that%20incident%20was%20terminated%20as%20a%20result%20of%20an%20investigation%20and%20the%20direct%20manager%20who%20failed%20to%20escalate%20the%20matter%20was%20disciplined%2C%26quot%3B%20Costiglio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20a%20new%20class%20of%20young%20colleagues%20joined%20around%202018%2C%20bankers%20prepared%20for%20their%20arrival%20by%20circulating%20a%20dossier%20that%20included%20their%20photos.%20Employees%20judged%20their%20attractiveness%20and%20openly%20discussed%20favorites%2C%20according%20to%20one%20person%20who%20saw%20it%20and%20two%20others%20who%20heard%20of%20it%20at%20the%20time.%20A%20similar%20account%20was%20included%20in%20last%20November's%20lawsuit%20from%20Ardith%20Lindsey%2C%20the%20managing%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20as%20the%20division%20continued%20to%20deal%20with%20underperformance%2C%20Fater%20Belbachir%20was%20brought%20in%20as%20equities%20chief.%20Yet%20problems%20persisted.%20After%20a%20hot%20streak%20in%202021%2C%20a%20London%20staffer's%20fat-finger%20trade%20sparked%20a%20flash%20crash%20in%20European%20stocks%2C%20a%20blow%20for%20Fraser%20and%20Belbachir%2C%20who%20still%20runs%20the%20unit.%20Lindsey's%20lawsuit%20alleged%20that%20he%20ignored%20women%20and%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20male%20managers%20that%20bonded%20by%20discussing%20sexual%20conquests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reference%20to%20Mr.%20Belbachir%20is%20based%20on%20an%20unsubstantiated%20claim%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20Citi%20is%20strongly%20contesting%2C%26quot%3B%20Costiglio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20male%20managers%20was%20Mani%20Singh%2C%20an%20executive%20who%20coerced%20Lindsey%20into%20a%20relationship%20and%20threatened%20her%20and%20her%20children%2C%20Lindsey%20said%20in%20her%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20questioned%20several%20years%20ago%20about%20a%20large%20financial%20transaction%20between%20them%2C%20Ms.%20Lindsey%20described%20Mr.%20Singh%20as%20only%20a%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20Costiglio%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20later%20told%20the%20bank%20that%20the%20relationship%20was%20consensual.%20It%20couldn't%20have%20been%2C%20according%20to%20Lindsey's%20attorney%2C%20because%20of%20the%20difference%20in%20power%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lindsey%20formally%20complained%2C%20Costiglio%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20immediately%20placed%20Mr.%20Singh%20on%20leave%20and%20began%20an%20investigation.%20Mr.%20Singh%20resigned%20within%20days%2C%20before%20the%20investigation%20could%20be%20completed.%26quot%3B%20Singh%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELindsey's%20complaint%20depicted%20an%20environment%20where%20men%20talked%20about%20which%20women%20they%20wanted%20to%20sleep%20with%2C%20treating%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20objects.%26quot%3B%20In%20interviews%20with%20Bloomberg%20News%20after%20her%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%2C%20five%20women%20who've%20worked%20in%20the%20division%20described%20similar%20experiences%20of%20men%20ogling%20them%20as%20they%20walked%20the%20trading%20floor%20as%20recently%20as%202019.%20Three%20said%20they%20were%20also%20upset%20by%20Singh's%20behavior%20toward%20them%3A%20One%20junior%20employee%2C%20for%20example%2C%20said%20he%20would%20drop%20his%20credit%20card%20in%20front%20of%20her%20to%20request%20she%20fetch%20him%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20bleak%20episode%20contributed%20to%20the%20sense%20that%20the%20division%20protected%20an%20in-crowd.%20When%20a%20top%20trader%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20a%20charge%20of%20driving%20while%20intoxicated%20with%20a%20child%20in%20his%20car%2C%20Citigroup%20asked%20regulators%20not%20to%20disqualify%20him%2C%20industry%20records%20show.%20The%20bank%20did%20not%20remove%20the%20trader%2C%20who%20still%20works%20there%2C%20from%20top%20accounts%2C%20including%20the%20billionaire%20Steve%20Cohen's%20hedge%20fund%2C%20five%20colleagues%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wall%20Street%2C%20bankers%20and%20traders%20have%20long%20used%20drugs%2C%20but%20their%20prevalence%20in%20this%20group%20stood%20out%20to%20employees%20who've%20worked%20at%20other%20firms.%20Bankers%20did%20cocaine%20at%20the%20company's%20Manhattan%20headquarters%20and%20with%20colleagues%20and%20clients%20outside%20it%2C%20according%20to%20three%20people%20who%20saw%20it%20themselves.%20One%20member%20of%20the%20team%20said%20she%20was%20at%20her%20desk%20on%20the%20trading%20floor%20around%202016%20when%20she%20saw%20a%20coworker%20with%20white%20residue%20between%20his%20nose%20and%20lip.%20She%20suggested%20he%20wipe%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20recently%20taken%20steps%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20bad%20behaviour.%20Last%20month%2C%20Citigroup%20told%20its%20investment%20bank's%20dealmakers%20to%20rein%20in%20their%20drinking%20at%20client%20events%2C%20reminding%20them%20to%20keep%20the%20firm's%20reputation%20in%20mind%20after%20complaints%20of%20unruliness.%20And%20a%20senior%20dealmaker%20in%20its%20equity%20capital%20markets%20group%20was%20put%20on%20leave%20this%20year%20amid%20an%20investigation%20into%20a%20verbal%20altercation%20with%20a%20junior%20banker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFraser%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20bank's%20biggest%20overhaul%20in%20decades.%20She's%20trying%20to%20shrink%20the%20lender%20after%20it%20became%20one%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20most%20bloated%20institutions%2C%20with%20missed%20financial%20goals%20and%20a%20stock%20price%20that%20trails%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rotator%20who%20went%20to%20Catch%20and%20was%20told%20to%20shorten%20her%20skirts%20recalled%20going%20to%20Salima%20Habib%2C%20a%20move%20that%20three%20others%20said%20they%20heard%20about%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rotator%20recalls%20Habib%20saying%20she'd%20have%20to%20tell%20a%20manager%20and%20also%20offering%20advice%3A%20going%20directly%20to%20HR%20was%20another%20option%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20arduous%2C%20or%20the%20younger%20woman%20could%20try%20confronting%20the%20man%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20comments%20attributed%20to%20Ms.%20Habib%20by%20unnamed%20sources%20have%20been%20mischaracterized%20and%20are%20not%20consistent%20with%20her%20record%20of%20supporting%20and%20empowering%20women%20throughout%20her%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rotator%20also%20remembers%20Habib%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20promoted%20to%20run%20sales%20in%20the%20US%20for%20the%20division%2C%20offering%20her%20one%20more%20recommendation%3A%20Try%20to%20meditate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711259220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ff1ls8an_citigroup_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-drug-culture-harassment-plagued-a-citigroup-division-for-years-5300522%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bankers%20from%20Citigroup%20Inc.%20were%20partying%20with%20clients%20one%20night%20in%20May%202018%20at%20a%20downtown%20Manhattan%20hot%20spot%20called%20Catch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-drug-culture-harassment-plagued-a-citigroup-division-for-years-5300522%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%20About%20Ghost%20Jobs%2C%20The%20Rising%20Trend%20In%20Hiring%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20rising%20trend%20of%20ghost%20jobs%20has%20gained%20significant%20attention%20after%20a%20social%20media%20user%20shared%20a%20personal%20anecdote.%C2%A0These%20are%20jobs%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Copen%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20company%20website%20but%20don't%20actually%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%2C%20Maureen%20W%20Clough%2C%20shared%20a%20note%20on%20Thread%2C%20where%20she%20revealed%20that%20the%20HR%20personnel%20of%20her%20company%20asked%20her%20to%20continue%20interviewing%20candidates%20for%20a%20ghost%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20details%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere's%20a%20new%20super%20cool%20trend%20in%20tech%3A%20ghost%20jobs...%20I%20was%20a%20hiring%20manager%20with%20a%20new%20position%20to%20fill.%20As%20I%20went%20through%20the%20process%20with%20candidates%2C%20a%20buddy%20said%2C%20'Hey%2C%20do%20you%20know%20there's%20a%20hiring%20freeze%3F'%20I%20went%20to%20HR%2C%20who%20confirmed%E2%80%A6%20then%20told%20me%20to%20keep%20going%20with%20interviews%20since%20the%20req%20%E2%80%9Cmight%E2%80%9D%20be%20reopened.%20NOPE.%20I%20refused%20to%20waste%20candidates'%20time%20%26amp%3B%20my%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40maureenwclough%2Fpost%2FC4iu0jwxGK5%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40maureenwclough%2Fpost%2FC4iu0jwxGK5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40maureenwclough%2Fpost%2FC4iu0jwxGK5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPost%20by%20%40maureenwclough%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40maureenwclough%2Fpost%2FC4iu0jwxGK5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20Ghost%20Job%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhost%20jobs%20are%20the%20vacancies%20that%20a%20company%20advertises%20but%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20filling.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20may%20vary%20from%20company%20to%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20possible%20explanation%20is%20that%20a%20company%20may%20be%20unable%20to%20budget%20for%20hiring%20new%20employees%20during%20that%20specific%20period%2C%20while%20another%20reason%20could%20be%20to%20assess%20the%20talent%20pool%20available%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20possibility%20that%20these%20%E2%80%9Copen%20jobs%E2%80%9D%20have%20been%20posted%20earlier%20for%20an%20upcoming%20position%2C%20which%20is%20not%20currently%20available%20or%20will%20not%20exist%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20that%20freeze%20the%20hiring%20process%20still%20have%20job%20postings%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20study%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hbs.edu%2Fmanaging-the-future-of-work%2FDocuments%2Fresearch%2Fhiddenworkers09032021.pdf%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Business%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20employees%20quitting%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20its%20economic%20uncertainty%20might%20have%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20ghost%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20added%20that%20it%20might%20be%20due%20to%20companies%20being%20unsure%20of%20the%20future%20and%20hiring%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20several%20ghost%20job%20listings%20don't%20even%20have%20a%20job%20description%20but%20include%20a%20long%20list%20of%20perks%20to%20convince%20a%20candidate%20to%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20you%20tell%20if%20the%20job%20is%20real%20or%20not%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenuine%20job%20postings%20will%20always%20include%20specific%20details%20about%20the%20expectations%20for%20the%20role%2C%20qualifications%20and%20responsibilities.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20a%20candidate%20comes%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fkaradennison%2F2023%2F11%2F27%2Fhow-ghost-job-postings-are-creating-a-false-sense-of-hope%2F%3Fsh%3D398860057dc0%5C%22%3Ea%20vague%20job%20description%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20reads%20like%20a%20generic%20template%2C%20then%20that%20is%20your%20clue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20candidate%20applies%20for%20a%20job%20and%20doesn't%20get%20a%20response%20for%20weeks%20or%20even%20months%20in%20some%20cases%20then%20that%20means%20he%2Fshe%20fell%20for%20a%20ghost%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20candidate%20comes%20across%20the%20same%20job%20opening%20repeatedly%20over%20an%20extended%20period%20could%20also%20serve%20as%20a%20warning%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711259160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fj67moja8_job-interview-generic_625x300_10_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-ghost-jobs-the-rising-trend-in-hiring-5300521%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghost%20jobs%20are%20vacancies%20that%20a%20company%20advertises%20about%20but%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20filling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-ghost-jobs-the-rising-trend-in-hiring-5300521%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Governance%20In%20Action%3A%20On%20AAP's%20Approach%20To%20Empowering%20Women%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Frft8pta_delhi-women-bus-ride-twitter_625x300_03_November_19.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202019%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Faap%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal-led%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20government%20enabled%20women%20to%20travel%20in%20buses%20free%20of%20cost%20-%20AC%20buses%20included%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhis-pink-ticket-scheme-is-more-than-just-a-free-bus-ride-2126485%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20'pink%20ticket'%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20wasn't%20just%20to%20make%20transportation%20convenient%2C%20but%20also%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20and%20progress%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fwont-be-tolerated-arvind-kejriwal-warns-action-against-drivers-who-dont-stop-buses-for-women-4045029%5C%22%3Ewomen%20across%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Addressing%20gender%20disparities%20in%20urban%20transit%20helps%20create%20a%20safe%20and%20economical%20commuting%20option%20for%20women%20while%20also%20symbolising%20a%20larger%20commitment%20to%20their%20empowerment%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20The%20step%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20transformative.%20Be%20it%20for%20education%2C%20employment%20or%20leisure%2C%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20female%20ridership%20in%20buses%2C%20a%20jump%20from%2033%25%20to%20roughly%2044%25.%20Currently%2C%20approximately%2011%20lakh%20women%20travel%20for%20free%20in%20Delhi's%20buses%20every%20day.%20More%20than%20100%20crore%20pink%20tickets%20were%20sold%20as%20of%20February%202023%2C%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20spending%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20on%20the%20scheme.%20Moreover%2C%20safety%20measures%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmcd-schools-to-get-10-786-cctv-cameras-4633278%5C%22%3ECCTV%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20panic%20buttons%2C%20and%20vehicle%20tracking%20systems%20are%20installed%20in%2096%25%20of%20operational%20buses%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20sense%20of%20security%20for%20women%20as%20they%20traverse%20the%20city.%20A%20greater%20presence%20of%20women%20in%20public%20spaces%20also%20builds%20safer%20spaces%20for%20other%20women%2C%20who%20feel%20encouraged%20to%20step%20out%20and%20pursue%20their%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Changing%20Economic%20Landscape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20the%20free%20bus%20transportation%20scheme%20for%20women%20has%20also%20acted%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20enhancing%20their%20labour%20force%20participation%2C%20thereby%20helping%20the%20economic%20strain%20on%20low-income%20households%20and%20helping%20bridge%20the%20gender%20divide%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20This%20has%20also%20contributed%20to%20Delhi's%20economic%20landscape%2C%20which%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20surge%20in%20per%20capita%20income%20from%20%E2%82%B92.47%20lakh%20per%20annum%20in%202014%20to%20%E2%82%B94.62%20lakh%20per%20annum%20currently%2C%20nearly%20doubling%20and%20surpassing%20the%20national%20average%20by%202.5%20times.%20Contrary%20to%20misinformed%20claims%20that%20%26quot%3Bfree%20bus%20rides%20is%20bad%20economics%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20fiscal%20prudence%20has%20ensured%20a%20surplus%20budget%2C%20which%20underscores%20the%20financial%20stability%20of%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20today%2C%20the%20winds%20of%20change%20continue%20to%20blow%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-the-eligibility-criteria-for-mukhyamantri-mahila-samman-yojana-announced-by-aap-5173327%5C%22%3EMukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Delhi%20budget%202024-2025.%20This%20scheme%20aims%20to%20help%20millions%20of%20women%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20come%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds.%20By%20offering%20financial%20assistance%20for%20personal%20and%20professional%20development%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20bolster%20women's%20socio-economic%20independence.%20It%20extends%20financial%20support%20to%20women%20who%20have%20historically%20faced%20barriers%2C%20thus%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20society%20where%20women%20can%20thrive%20independently.%20With%20this%20initiative%2C%20women%20are%20empowered%20to%20break%20free%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20financial%20dependence%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20pursue%20their%20aspirations.%20It%20heralds%20a%20new%20dawn%20of%20progress%20for%20women%20in%20the%20city%2C%20bringing%20us%20closer%20to%20a%20reality%20where%20gender%20equality%20isn't%20just%20an%20aspiration%20but%20a%20lived%20experience%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Girl%20Student%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20is%20just%20one%20facet%20of%20Delhi's%20approach%20to%20women's%20empowerment%2C%20which%20builds%20upon%20the%20foundation%20of%20past%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20fostering%20progress%20in%20various%20domains.%20For%20instance%2C%20under%20%C2%A0AAP%2C%20the%20capital's%20government%20schools%20are%20today%20providing%20world-class%20education%20to%20over%209%20lakh%20girls.%20Many%20of%20them%20often%20outperform%20their%20male%20counterparts.%20Initiatives%20such%20as%20free%20textbooks%2C%20uniforms%2C%20and%20specialised%20STEM%20education%20for%20them%20ensure%20that%20no%20girl%20is%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20knowledge%20and%20opportunities.%20This%20year%2C%20933%20girls%20from%20Delhi%20government%20schools%20cleared%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%2C%20while%20123%20made%20the%20cut%20in%20the%20JEE%20exam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20commitment%20to%20women's%20health%2C%20too%2C%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20establishment%20and%20expansion%20of%20accessible%20healthcare%20facilities%20like%20the%20women-centric%20Mahila%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20which%20cater%20to%20women's%20needs%20specifically%2C%20alongside%20the%20regular%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20and%20Anganwadi%20Hubs.%20These%20initiatives%20have%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20improving%20medical%20outcomes%20for%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20marginalised%20sections%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20woman%20has%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare%20services%20in%20her%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen's%20Safety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20aren't%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20elected%20government%2C%20with%202.60%20lakh%20CCTV%20cameras%20under%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20CCTV%20Scheme%20(that%20is%2C%201%2C820%20cameras%20per%20square%20mile)%2C%2087%2C000%20streetlights%20on%20roads%20and%202.80%20lakh%20LED%20street%20lights%20installed%20within%20colonies%20under%20the%20Mukhyamantri%20Delhi%20Street%20Lights%20Scheme%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20safety%20for%20women%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kejriwal%20government%20is%20also%20providing%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%2024x7%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20ease%20monthly%20expenditure%20concerns%20for%20women%20in%20many%20households.%20It%20has%20championed%20women's%20economic%20empowerment%20through%20initiatives%20that%20promote%20entrepreneurship%2C%20self-help%20groups%2C%20and%20access%20to%20microfinance%20loans.%20This%20comprehensive%20approach%20has%20not%20only%20uplifted%20individual%20women%20but%20is%20also%20contributing%20to%20a%20positive%20change%20within%20families%20and%20communities%2C%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20fostering%20a%20culture%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeading%20By%20Example%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20gender%20mainstreaming%20and%20gender-responsive%20budgeting%20and%20planning%20serves%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20governance%20in%20action.%20It%20can%20set%20an%20example%20for%20other%20governments%20too.%20By%20investing%20in%20women's%20health%2C%20education%2C%20safety%2C%20social%20mobility%20and%20economic%20empowerment%2C%20the%20city%20is%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20future%20where%20every%20woman%20can%20realise%20her%20full%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20other%20regions%20strive%20to%20emulate%20Delhi's%20successes%2C%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20evident%20that%20prioritising%20women's%20empowerment%20isn't%20just%20a%20moral%20imperative-it's%20essential%20for%20building%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20prosperous%20future%20for%20all.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20an%20advocate%20and%20senior%20AAP%20leader)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Frft8pta_delhi-women-bus-ride-twitter_625x300_03_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fgovernance-in-action-on-aaps-approach-to-empowering-women-in-delhi-5300555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20gender%20mainstreaming%20and%20gender-responsive%20budgeting%20and%20planning%20serves%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20governance%20in%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fgovernance-in-action-on-aaps-approach-to-empowering-women-in-delhi-5300555%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20CM%20Kejriwal%20issues%20first%20direction%20on%20running%20govt%20from%20ED%20custody%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F22%2Ffull%2F1711084671-2482.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fde