his%20stance%20marks%20a%20potential%20shift%20in%20Pakistan's%20diplomatic%20approach%20towards%20India%2C%20following%20tensions%20over%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370.%20Pakistan%20has%20maintained%20that%20India%20must%20reverse%20its%20actions%20in%20Kashmir%20as%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20dialogue%2C%20a%20demand%20that%20India%20has%20rejected%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fseriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister%2Farticleshow%2F108744325.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fseriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F108744325.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fseriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F108744325.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NCERT%20Set%20To%20Release%20New%20Textbooks%2C%20Syllabus%20For%20CBSE%20Classes%203%2C%206%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20announcement%2C%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20has%20communicated%20that%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20will%20be%20introducing%20new%20syllabi%20and%20textbooks%20for%20classes%203%20and%206%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202024-25%2C%20starting%20April%201.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20classes%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20existing%20curriculum%20and%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%2C%20in%20a%20communique%20sent%20to%20all%20affiliated%20institutions%2C%20stated%20that%20NCERT%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20March%2018%2C%20has%20revealed%20its%20ongoing%20development%20of%20new%20syllabi%20and%20textbooks%20for%20classes%20third%20and%20sixth.%20Schools%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20transition%20to%20these%20new%20materials%2C%20replacing%20NCERT-published%20textbooks%20until%20the%20year%202023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20initiatives%20are%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20framework%20outlined%20in%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20new%20national%20curriculum%20framework%20for%20school%20education%20(NCF-SE)%202023.%20As%20per%20the%20CBSE%20statement%2C%20a%20bridge%20course%20for%20class%20six%20and%20concise%20guidelines%20for%20class%20three%20are%20in%20the%20works%20to%20facilitate%20a%20smooth%20transition%20aligned%20with%20NCF-SE%202023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BA%20bridge%20course%20for%20class%206%2C%20and%20concise%20guidelines%20for%20class%203%20are%20being%20developed%20by%20NCERT%20for%20facilitating%20a%20seamless%20transition%20for%20students%20to%20new%20pedagogical%20practices%20and%20areas%20of%20study%20aligned%20with%20NCF-SE%202023.%20These%20resources%20will%20be%20disseminated%20to%20all%20the%20schools%20online%20once%20they%20are%20received%20from%20NCERT%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20CBSE%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20conduct%20capacity-building%20programs%20for%20school%20heads%20and%20teachers%2C%20aimed%20at%20familiarising%20them%20with%20the%20new%20teaching-learning%20methodologies%20envisaged%20in%20NEP-2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20Curriculum%20and%20textbooks%20for%20other%20classes%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202024-25%20commencing%20from%20April%201%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CBSE%20said.%20Schools%20have%20been%20urged%20to%20adopt%20the%20recommendations%20outlined%20in%20NCF-SE%202023%2C%20incorporating%20methodologies%20like%20multilingualism%2C%20art-integrated%20education%2C%20and%20experiential%20learning%20where%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSchools%20are%20advised%20to%20align%20their%20practices%20with%20the%20recommendations%20delineated%20in%20NCF-SE-2023.%20This%20includes%20adherence%20to%20guidelines%20concerning%20content%2C%20pedagogical%20strategies%2C%20assessment%20methodologies%2C%20and%20other%20pertinent%20areas%20as%20communicated%20by%20the%20board%20from%20time%20to%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20follows%20NCERT's%20rationalisation%20of%20syllabi%20for%20classes%206%20to%2012%20in%202022%2C%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20the%20content%20load%20on%20students%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20Notable%20changes%20included%20the%20removal%20of%20chapters%20on%20various%20historical%20and%20political%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-05%2Fu55173rg_cbsekids_650x400_08_May_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fncert-set-to-release-new-textbooks-syllabus-for-cbse-classes-3-6-5300711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CBSE%20said%20there%20would%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20curriculum%20and%20textbooks%20for%20other%20classes%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202024-25%20starting%20April%201%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fncert-set-to-release-new-textbooks-syllabus-for-cbse-classes-3-6-5300711%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22University%20students%20become%20tram%20operators%20as%20Germany%20faces%20manpower%20shortage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711257846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108744453%2Cimgsize-534230.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funiversity-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage%2Farticleshow%2F108743993.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Ci