ly%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20can%20do%20this%20because%20he%20considers%20himself%20a%20family%20member%20of%20Delhi's%202%20crore%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20BJP%2C%20you%20can%20arrest%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20put%20him%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20you%20cannot%20imprison%20his%20love%20and%20sense%20of%20duty%20for%20Delhi's%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader%20may%20be%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bno%20work%20will%20stop%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20out%20the%20letter%2C%20she%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20ji%20has%20written%2C%20'I%20have%20come%20to%20know%20that%20some%20areas%20of%20Delhi%20are%20facing%20water%20supply%20and%20sewer%20problems.%20I%20am%20worried%20about%20this.%20People%20should%20not%20face%20any%20problem%20because%20I%20am%20in%20jail.%20Summer%20is%20here%2C%20so%20please%20ensure%20adequate%20tankers%20in%20areas%20facing%20water%20shortage.%20Please%20give%20directions%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20other%20officials%20so%20that%20people%20face%20no%20difficulty.%20People%20should%20get%20immediate%20and%20proper%20solution%20to%20their%20problems.%20Please%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20if%20needed.%20He%20will%20surely%20help%20you'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20today%2C%20after%20being%20arrested%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20ji%20is%20thinking%20about%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Atishi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20ED%20on%20Thursday%20night%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%2C%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20the%20central%20agency's%20custody%20for%20a%20week.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20for%20political%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20Chief%20Minister%20despite%20his%20arrest.%20While%20no%20law%20bars%20him%2C%20prison%20rules%20will%20make%20it%20very%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20law%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%20says%20an%20inmate%20can%20hold%20only%20two%20meetings%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRunning%20a%20government%20from%20jail%20is%20not%20straightforward.%20The%20jail%20manual%20states%20that%20you%20can%20meet%20your%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20or%20associates%20only%20twice%20a%20week.%20So%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20govern%20with%20these%20restrictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gupta%20has%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20one%20way%20out.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20can%20carry%20on%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20he%20can%20get%20authorities%20to%20put%20him%20under%20house%20arrest.%20This%20would%2C%20however%2C%20require%20an%20approval%20from%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Administrator%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20declare%20any%20building%20as%20a%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20past%20instances%20where%20court%20complexes%20were%20designated%20as%20temporary%20jails.%20Such%20measures%20could%20help%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20continue%20to%20run%20the%20government%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20an%20order%20from%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20seems%20unlikely%2C%20given%20the%20history%20of%20face-offs%20between%20the%20Centre's%20nominee%20and%20the%20AAP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20is%20examining%20ramifications%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20not%20resigning.%20Legal%20experts%20said%20the%20Centre%20may%20have%20to%20suspend%20or%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20post%20since%20he%20is%20a%20public%20servant.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20procedure%20that%20is%20followed%20for%20government%20officials%20who%20are%20arrested.%20They%20are%20immediately%20suspended%20from%20service%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20fourth%20high-profile%20arrest%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20after%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20leader%20K%20Kavitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711257120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1o4sf5l8_arvind-kejriwal-ani_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-issues-his-1st-order-from-enforcement-directorate-lock-up-5300295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20debate%20on%20whether%20he%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20as%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20from%20prison%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20issued%20his%20first%20order%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20(ED)%20lock-up%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-issues-his-1st-order-from-enforcement-directorate-lock-up-5300295%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20cues%2C%20FII%20activity%20to%20guide%20stock%20markets%20next%20week%2C%20say%20Analysts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711256373000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F16%2Ffull%2F1710556617-349.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fglobal-cues-fii-activity-to-guide-stock-markets-next-week-say-analysts-124032400108_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Movement%20in%20global%20oil%20benchmark%20Brent%20crude%20and%20rupee-dollar%20trend%20would%20also%20be%20watched%20by%20investors%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%