2F2024%2Fscene%2Fnews%2Fjill-biden-human-rights-campaign-gaza-ceasefire-protestors-lgbtq-1235950511%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KKR%20Star%20Handed%20Stern%20Penalty%20For%20IPL%20Code%20Of%20Conduct%20Breach%20vs%20SRH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20star%20Harshit%20Rana%20has%20been%20handed%20a%20stringent%20penalty%20for%20breaching%20the%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20match%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20fine%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20the%20KKR%20pacer%20because%20of%20his%20send-offs%20to%20SRH%20stars%20Mayank%20Agarwal%20and%20Heinrich%20Klaasen.%20The%20young%20Knight%20Riders%20seamer%20emerged%20as%20the%20match-winner%20against%20the%20Sunrisers%2C%20especially%20with%20his%20final%20over%20heroics.%20But%2C%20his%20conduct%20left%20many%20disappointed%2C%20with%20IPL%20deducting%2060%20percent%20of%20his%20match%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20bowler%20Harshit%20Rana%20has%20been%20fined%20a%20total%20of%2060%20percent%20of%20his%20match%20fees%20for%20breaching%20the%20IPL%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20during%20his%20team's%20Tata%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20match%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20at%20Eden%20Gardens%2C%20Kolkata%20on%20March%2023.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BRana%20committed%20two%20Level%201%20offences%20under%20Article%202.5%20of%20the%20IPL's%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20He%20was%20fined%2010%20percent%20and%2050%20percent%20of%20his%20match%20fees%20for%20the%20two%20respective%20offences.%20Rana%20admitted%20to%20the%20two%20offences%20and%20accepted%20the%20Match%20Referee's%20sanction.%20For%20Level%201%20breaches%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20the%20Match%20Referee's%20decision%20is%20final%20and%20binding%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20release%20from%20IPL%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20managed%20to%20keep%20SRH%20at%20bay%20while%20defending%2013%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over%20as%20KKR%20emerged%20triumphant%20by%204%20runs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20an%20all-round%20show%20from%20Andre%20Russell%2C%20KKR%20were%20almost%20crushed%20by%20a%20one-man-show%20by%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%2C%20before%20Harshit%20defended%2013%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20match%2C%20KKR%20captain%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%2C%20%26quot%3BRight%20from%20the%2017th%20over%2C%20had%20butterflies%20in%20my%20stomach.%20Felt%20anything%20could%20happen%20in%20the%20last%20over.%20They%20needed%2013%20runs%20and%20we%20didn't%20have%20the%20most%20experienced%20bowler.%20But%20I%20had%20the%20belief%20in%20him%20(Harshit)%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20to%20back%20himself%20and%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20happens.%20He%20was%20a%20bit%20nervous%20coming%20in%2C%20and%20I%20just%20looked%20him%20in%20the%20eye%20and%20told%20him%20'this%20is%20your%20moment%2C%20buddy.'%20Told%20him%20to%20back%20himself%20and%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20talking%20about%20performances%20of%20Russell%20and%20Sunil%20Narine%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20not%20giving%20a%20boundary%20in%20his%20spell%2C%20Narine%20said%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20such%20experience.%20Great%20to%20see%20Andre%20perform%20with%20bat%20and%20ball%2C%20and%20even%20Sunny%20(Narine)%20was%20splendid%20with%20the%20ball.%20Fantastic%20to%20have%20them%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways%20gives%20you%20motivation%20when%20you%20start%20with%20a%20win.%20This%20game%20also%20gives%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20learnings%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20we%20will%20take%20from%20this%20ground.%20I%20think%20fielding%20is%20an%20area%20we%20need%20to%20improve%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20Iyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17112