20Congress%20leader%20Shanti%20Dhariwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20president%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%20maintained%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20induct%20Gunjal%20was%20unanimously%20supported%20by%20all%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20Dhariwal%2C%20who%20shares%20a%20bitter%20relationship%20with%20Gunjal%2C%20was%20conspicuously%20missing%20from%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20induction%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Congress%20office%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defection%20of%20Gunjal%20just%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20shows%20the%20larger%20trend%20in%20both%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20opposition%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20wherein%20both%20the%20parties%20are%20relying%20on%20turncoats%20from%20other%20political%20parties%20to%20get%20the%20electoral%20arithmetic%20right%20in%20the%20state%20with%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal%20politician%20quitting%20Congress%2C%20Jat%20politician%20leaving%20BJP%20over%20feud%20with%20Rajput%20leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20February%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20the%20first%20move%20by%20inducting%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20senior%20politician%20Mahendrajeet%20Singh%20Malviya%20into%20its%20ranks%20and%20declaring%20him%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20from%20the%20tribal%20dominated%20Banswara%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20where%20apart%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP)%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20potent%20political%20force%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20was%20quick%20to%20hit%20back%2C%20as%20Rahul%20Kaswan%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20incumbent%20MP%20from%20Churu%20joined%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Subsequently%20he%20has%20been%20fielded%20by%20the%20Congress%20from%20the%20Churu%20seat%2C%20which%20Kaswan%20has%20won%20twice%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Kaswan%E2%80%99s%20family%20%E2%80%94%20his%20father%20Ram%20Singh%20Kaswan%20is%20also%20a%20former%20MP%20from%20Churu%20%E2%80%94%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress%20fold%20after%20the%20BJP%20denied%20a%20ticket%20to%20him%20and%20instead%20fielded%20Paralympian%20Devendra%20Jhajharia%20from%20the%20seat%2C%20making%20the%20contest%20for%20Churu%20one%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20electoral%20battles%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20denial%20of%20ticket%20to%20Kaswan%20by%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20feud%20with%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Rajendra%20Rathore%2C%20a%20former%20seven-time%20MLA%20who%20was%20also%20the%20Rajasthan%20leader%20of%20opposition%20before%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathore%2C%20a%20Rajput%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Kaswan%20family%2C%20which%20is%20from%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%20have%20decided%20the%20course%20of%20Churu%E2%80%99s%20politics%20in%20the%20last%20three%20decades%2C%20also%20strengthening%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20district.%20While%20Rathore%20was%20elected%20an%20MLA%20from%20seats%20in%20Churu%20district%20consecutively%20for%20seven%20times%20between%201990%20and%202023%2C%20the%20Churu%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20been%20held%20by%20a%20Kaswan%20family%20member%20since%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20camaraderie%20between%20Rathore%20and%20the%20Kaswan%20clan%20suffered%20after%20Rathore%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%20from%20the%20Taranagar%20Assembly%20constituency%2C%20where%20Narendra%20Budania%2C%20a%20senior%20Congress%20MLA%20emerged%20victorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathore%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20alleged%20that%20the%20Kaswan%20family%20was%20responsible%20for%20Rathore%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20by%20helping%20Congress%20candidate%20Budania%20and%20backstabbing%20Rathore%20in%20the%20electoral%20arena.%20Rathore%20himself%20termed%20those%20who%20%E2%80%98betrayed%E2%80%99%20him%20as%20%E2%80%98Jaichand%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20sitting%20MP%20Kaswan%20was%20denied%20a%20ticket%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20counter%20attack%20by%20Rathore%2C%20who%20holds%20considerable%20influence%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Kaswan%20joined%20Congress%2C%20the%20electoral%20battle%20in%20Churu%20has%20become%20a%20Jat%20vs%20Rajput%20fight%2C%20with%20Kaswan%20against%20Jhajharia%2C%20who%20despite%20being%20a%20Jat%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20proxy%20candidate%20for%20Rathore%2C%20a%20Rajput.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBehind%20defections%3A%20Focus%20on%20OBC%20votes%2C%20shrinking%20space%20for%20Raje%20loyalists%20in%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20BJP%20inducted%20several%20OBC%20Congress%20leaders%20including%20former%20MLAs%20Richpal%20Mirdha%2C%20his%20son%20Vijaypal%20Mirdha%20and%20former%20ministers%20Lalchand%20Kataria%20and%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Richpal%20Mirdha%20and%20his%20son%20VIjaypal%20Mirdha%20belong%20from%20the%20Mirdha%20clan%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20Jat%20political%20families%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20Kataria%20and%20Yadav%20were%20close%20aides%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Kataria%20and%20Yadav%20were%20ministers%20in%20the%20previous%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government.%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20premises%20were%20also%20raided%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20mid%20day%20meal%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-an-adivasi-party-is-changing-political-equations-in-southern-rajasthans-tribal-districts%5C%22%3EHow%20an%20Adivasi%20Party%20is%20Changing%20Political%20Equations%20in%20Southern%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Tribal%20Districts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defections%20reflect%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20the%20Jat%20and%20OBC%20votes%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20has%20been%20winning%20all%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJat%20leaders%20such%20as%20Mirdha%20and%20Kataria%20wield%20significant%20influence%20in%20districts%20such%20as%20Nagaur%20and%20Jaipur%20rural%20from%20where%20they%20have%20been%20elected%20as%20legislators%20and%20parliamentarians%2C%20while%20Yadav%20was%20among%20the%20most%20well%20known%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20from%20the%20Yadav%20community%2C%20who%20are%20traditional%20voters%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20inducting%20strong%20OBC%20and%20Jats%20leaders%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20strengthen%20its%20grip%20in%20districts%20such%20as%20Nagaur%2C%20where%20the%20Jat%20votes%20decides%20the%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20by%20fielding%20BJP%20turncoat%20Kaswan%2C%20the%20Congress%20hopes%20to%20give%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20Churu%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Shekhawati%20region.%20Even%20though%20the%20Congress%20lost%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20it%20had%20outperformed%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Shekhawati%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyeing%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Western%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20declared%20Umeda%20Ram%20Beniwal%20a%20turncoat%20from%20the%20Hanuman%20Beniwal-led%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%20(RLP)%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20the%20Jat%20dominated%20Barmer%20parliamentary%20seat.%20Beniwal%20will%20take%20on%20Union%20Minister%20Kailash%20Choudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20has%20seen%20a%20leadership%20change%20is%20also%20instrumental%20behind%20its%20established%20leaders%20joining%20the%20Congress.%20Seasoned%20BJP%20politicians%20such%20as%20%C2%A0Kaswan%20and%20Gunjal%20were%20counted%20among%20staunch%20supporters%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Raje%2C%20who%20was%20not%20given%20a%20third%20term%20by%20the