ears%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fonly-8-sensex-firms-disclosed-making-political-contribution-in-last-5-years-124032201044_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollectively%2C%20these%20companies%20spent%20Rs%20628%20crore%20on%20political%20contributions%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20said%2C%20citing%20their%20annual%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20telecom%20major%20Bharti%20Airtel%20contributed%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20Rs%20241%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20(Rs%20175%20crore)%20and%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(Rs%2085%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20Airtel%20emerged%20as%20the%20only%20Sensex%20company%20that%20consistently%20donated%20to%20political%20parties%20each%20year%2C%20in%20the%20past%20five%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20annual%20reports%2C%20the%20company%20and%20its%20subsidiaries%20collectively%20donated%20Rs%20241%20crore%20to%20political%20parties%20between%20FY19%20and%20FY23%2C%20either%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20or%20contributions%20to%20electoral%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20expenses%20include%20political%20contributions%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20300%20million%20(Rs%2030%20crore)%20and%20Rs%201%2C025%20million%20(Rs%20102.5%20crore)%20made%20under%20Section%20182%20of%20the%20Act%20(Companies%20Act%2C%202013)%20during%20the%20year%20ended%20March%2031%2C%202023%20and%20March%2031%2C%202022%20respectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bharti%20Airtel%20in%20its%20annual%20report%20for%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20other%20index%20companies%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20list%20only%20sporadically%20reported%20expenditures%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20or%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20in%20their%20annual%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20L