ha-polls%5C%22%3Earrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20and%20the%20main%20leader%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20once%20again%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20it%20would%20not%20allow%20any%20major%20political%20leader%20or%20party%20to%20remain%20in%20a%20position%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-arrest-likely-ed%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%2C%20was%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20another%20%E2%80%98corruption%E2%80%99%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20was%20imminent.%20The%20ED%20had%20been%20issuing%20summons%20to%20him%20and%20the%20courts%20refused%20to%20restrain%20the%20agency.%20Even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20burnt%20the%20midnight%20oil%20to%20save%20Arnab%20Goswami%E2%80%99s%20liberty%2C%20asked%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20not%20to%20disturb%20its%20sleep%20and%20come%20the%20next%20morning.%20Meanwhile%2C%20he%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20supposed%20to%20believe%20that%20all%20this%20is%20part%20of%20due%20process%20in%20investigating%20the%20alleged%20crime%20of%20changing%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20policy%20for%20monetary%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20leaders%20of%20the%20AAP%20have%20already%20been%20arrested%20and%20are%20in%20jail.%20Another%20leader%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20from%20Telangana%20is%20also%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20arrests%20of%20people%20like%20Anand%20Teltumbde%2C%20father%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20Hany%20Babu%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20and%20Umar%20Khalid%2C%20jurists%20have%20been%20asking%20again%20and%20again%20as%20to%20why%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20arrest%20people%20and%20keep%20them%20in%20jail%20only%20because%20it%20needs%20them