hat%20the%20government%20owns%20them%20and%20can%20do%20anything%20it%20wants%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20issued%20statements%20that%20all%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20bank%20accounts%20had%20been%20frozen%20and%20the%20party%20was%20left%20with%20no%20money%20to%20do%20even%20its%20basic%20organisational%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20reported%20that%20income%20tax%20officials%20went%20from%20bank%20to%20bank%20and%20arm%20twisted%20them%20to%20transfer%20money%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20step.%20We%20have%20not%20heard%20that%20banks%2C%20without%20even%20informing%20their%20clients%2C%20would%20allow%20their%20money%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20another%20account.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20the%20government%20is%20telling%20us%20that%20it%20owns%20everything%20we%20have.%20The%20government%20here%20is%20behaving%20like%20an%20extortionist.%20It%20can%20seize%20your%20account%2C%20it%20can%20take%20away%20money%20from%20it%20and%20it%20can%20arrest%20you%20when%20it%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20turning%20into%20mere%20properties%20of%20the%20government%20and%20do%20not%20realise%20what%20it%20is%20that%20we%20are%20losing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsLRO4qs6Q-Q%3Fsi%3D91h1qyULQm41LVus%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20runs%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20bipartisanship%20and%20the%20autonomy%20of%20institutions.%20It%20means%20the%20existence%20of%20an%20opposition%20and%20the%20acceptance%20by%20the%20government%20of%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20its%20voice%20and%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20we%20see%20is%20a%20BJP%20government%20which%20wants%20a%20political%20field%20empty%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20to%20be%20the%20only%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20it%20being%20done%20in%20the%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20winter%20session%2C%20in%20which%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20opposition%20was%20forced%20out.%20We%20saw%20the%20farcical%20proceedings%20of%20the%20cancellation%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20membership.%20Then%20we%20saw%20the%20blatant%20change%20in%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20selection%20of%20election%20commissioners.%20This%20is%20just%20before%20elections.%20And%20we%20saw%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20think%20that%20this%20is%20a%20football%20match%20or%20some%20kind%20of%20wrestling%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20government%2C%20we%20are%20mistaken.%20The%20opposition%20also%20represents%20the%20people.%20An%20election%20victory%20does%20not%20allow%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20disable%20the%20opposition%20by%20using%20the%20coercive%20instruments%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20knows%20that%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20or%20Hemant%20Soren%20is%20to%20scare%20political%20leaders%20and%20the%20people%20and%20stun%20them%20into%20inaction.%20It%20is%20also%20to%20stifle%20their%20voice%20when%20it%20is%20needed%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreezing%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20a%20party%20means%20freezing%20all%20of%20its%20movements.%20It%20cannot%20print%20a%20leaflet%2C%20its%20leaders%20cannot%20travel%20and%20its%20offices%20cannot%20function.%20But%20is%20it%20harming%20them%3F%20They%20function%20for%20us!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20good%20to%20hear%20what%20Salman%20Soz%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%2C%20said%20after%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20bank%20accounts%20were%20frozen%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20think%20it%20is%20just%20the%20problem%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%20that%20its%20accounts%20have%20been%20emptied%20out%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20then%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20how%20economies%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20have%20a%20snowball%20effect%20with%20businesses%20and%20individuals%20feeling%20insecure%20(remember%20the%20retrospective%20tax%3F).%20If%20the%20government%20can%20do%20it%20with%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20one%20which%20has%20the%20support%20of%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20imagine%20what%20the%20government%20can%20do%20to%20an%20individual%20company%20or%20taxpayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20you%20may%20say%20that%20I%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong%20and%20why%20will%20the%20government%20come%20after%20my%20business%20or%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20finances.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20how%20this%20works.%20Once%20this%20tiger%20tastes%20blood%2C%20its%20lust%20only%20grows.%20It%20looks%20for%20blood%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20already%20seen%20how%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20purchased%20by%20companies%20that%20were%20also%20raided%20by%20agencies.%20This%20will%20not%20remain%20confined%20to%20such%20companies%20but%20will%20keep%20spreading%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20anyone%20will%20remain%20immune%20from%20a%20feeling%20of%20insecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20we%20will%20live%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20those%20wielding%20power.%20Even%20when%20we%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong%2C%20and%20most%20people%20just%20want%20to%20live%20their%20lives%20peacefully%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20live%20according%20to%20the%20dictates%20of%20the%20Hafta%20Vasooli%20gang.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20how%20we%20want%20to%20live%3F%20Are%20we%20actors%20in%20this%20theatre%20of%20democracy%20or%20mere%20spectators%3F%20Have%20we%20turned%20into%20such%20imbeciles%20who%20get%20overawed%20by%20these%20strong-arm%20and%20clearly%20criminal%20acts%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power%20and%20clap%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20force%20the%20people%20to%20come%20out%20of%20their%20slumber%3F%20Will%20the%20streets%20wake%20up%3F%20For%20this%20is%20the%20moment%20for%20the%20people%20to%20rise%20and%20save%20the%20opposition.%20For%20its%20own%20sake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fapoorvanand%5C%22%3EApoorvanand%3C%2Fa%3E%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711123520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15115004%2FScreenshot-2023-11-15-at-11.49.15-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkejriwal-arrest-this-coup-against-our-constitutional-setup-is-a-wake-up-call%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20knows%20that%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20or%20Hemant%20Soren%20is%20to%20scare%20political%20leaders%20and%20the%20people%20and%20stun%20them%20into%20inaction.%20Is%20this%20how%20we%20want%20to%20live%3F%20Are%20we%20actors%20in%20this%20theatre%20of%20democracy%20or%20mere%20spectators%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkejriwal-arrest-this-coup-against-our-constitutional-setup-is-a-wake-up-call%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Congress%20No%20Exception%20in%20Wolfing%20Defectors%20for%20a%20Strong%20Lineup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22200254%2FSMR-II.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20is%20not%20immune%20to%2C%20what%20is%20by%20now%2C%20an%20accepted%20norm%20%E2%80%93%20fielding%20expatriates%20from%20rival%20parties%20as%20its%20candidates%20in%20the%20coming%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20out%20of%20five%20candidates%20announced%20by%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20in%20its%20third%20list%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2021)%20night%20are%20defectors%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS)%2C%20while%20the%20fourth%20is%20a%20rank%20outsider%20to%20politics%20who%20will%20make%20his%20debut%20in%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20even%20more%20surprising%20is%20that%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20Khairatabad%20MLA%2C%20Danam%20Nagender%2C%20who%20won%20the%20assembly%20polls%20only%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Congress%20even%20before%20he%20resigned%20from%20his%20former%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20four%20days%20after%20he%20posed%20for%20a%20photograph%20with%20chief%20minister%20and%20Telangana%20Congress%20committee%20president%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20while%20accepting%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20colours%2C%20he%20was%20declared%20its%20candidate%20from%20Secunderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20now%20petitioned%20assembly%20speaker%20G.%20Prasad%20Kumar%20seeking%20Nagender%E2%80%99s%20disqualification%20as%20per%20the%20anti-defection%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20BRS%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20G.%20Ranjith%20Reddy%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Chevella%20and%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20poultry%20industry%3B%20and%20G.%20Sunitha%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20who%20is%20the%20zilla%20parishad%20chairperson%20of%20Vikarabad%20district%20%E2%80%93%20also%20got%20tickets%20as%20Congress%20candidates%20from%20Chevella%20and%20Malkajgiri%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjith%20Reddy%20and%20Nagender%20joined%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunitha%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20wife%20of%20BRS%20MLC%20and%20former%20minister%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20was%20earlier%20sounded%20out%20for%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20from%20Chevella%20but%20was%20accommodated%20at%20Malkajgiri%2C%20reportedly%20against%20her%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Nagender%2C%20Mahender%20Reddy%20has%20also%20not%20resigned%20from%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Nagarkurnool%20(SC%20reserved)%20Mallu%20Ravi%20was%20renominated%20from%20the%20same%20constituency%20while%20Gaddam%20Vamshi%20Krishna%20was%20selected%20from%20Peddapalli%20(SC)%2C%20a%20constituency%20represented%20thrice%20by%20his%20grandfather%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Venkatswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20begin%20his%20political%20career%20straight%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Congress%20MLA%2C%20A.%20Sampath%20Kumar%20was%20overlooked%20for%20the%20Nagarkurnool%20seat%2C%20though%20he%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20former%20party%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20requesting%20his%20candidature%20to%20be%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20making%20a%20strong%20bid%20to%20repeat%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20has%20set%20its%20eyes%20on%20winning%20horses%20in%20its%20selection%20of%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20poured%20cold%20water%20on%20the%20ambition%20of%20former%20Hyderabad%20mayor%20Bonthu%20Rammohan%20and%20his%20wife%20Sridevi%2C%20a%20corporator%2C%20in%20getting%20a%20ticket%20from%20Secunderabad%20after%20the%20couple%20had%20quit%20the%20BRS%20last%20month%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20so%20far%20selected%20candidates%20for%20nine%20out%20of%2017%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20Telangana%20that%20will%20go%20to%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20played%20it%20safe%20in%20its%20earlier%20list%20of%20four%20candidates%20by%20selecting%20Vamshi%20Chand%20Reddy%20for%20Mahabubnagar%2C%20former%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20P.%20Balram%20Naik%20for%20Mahabubabad%2C%20former%20Congress%20legislature%20party%20leader%20K.%20Jana%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Raghuveer%20for%20Nalgonda%20and%20former%20MP%20Suresh%20Shetkar%20for%20Zaheerabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20got%20tickets%20on%20their%20home%20turfs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20became%20tough%20with%20leaders%20from%20the%20BRS%20joining%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20big%20way%20as%20the%20party%20consolidated%20its%20position%20after%20winning%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20that%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Copened%20the%20flood%20gates%E2%80%9D%20for%20entrants%20into%20the%20party%20received%20instant%20reactions%20from%20leaders%20like%20Nagender%20and%20Ranjith%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20trend%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20sources%20said%20more%20surprises%20were%20in%20store%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20remaining%20eight%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20stake%2C%20notably%2C%20was%20the%20selection%20for%20Nizamabad%20seat%2C%20where%20former%20minister%20T.%20Jeevan%20Reddy%20is%20a%20strong%20aspirant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20play%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20poaching%20candidates%20from%20the%20BRS%20to%20make%20its%20lineup%20strong.%20Both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20preying%20on%20the%20BRS%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20outsmart%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20gave%20tickets%20to%20two%20sitting%20MPs%2C%20two%20former%20MPs%20and%20a%20former%20MLA%20of%20the%20BRS%20who%20joined%20the%20party%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20contender%2C%20winning%20eight%20seats%20and%20obtaining%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2014%25%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20Congress%20won%2064%20seats%20and%20polled%2039.7%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20while%20the%20BRS%20won%2039%20seats%20and%20polled%2037.6%25%20of%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20assembly%20has%20119%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20gone%20up%20in%20the%20coming%20elections%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20BRS%20MLC%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20K.%20Kavitha%2C%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20were%20often%20confronted%20with%20questions%20on%20differential%20treatment%20for%20Kavitha%20by%20not%20arresting%20her%2C%20while%20the%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20languished%20in%20jail%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20expressed%20relief%20that%20the%20question%20did%20not%20haunt%20them%20anymore%20and%20that%20they%20could%20freely%20approach%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20K.%20Nageshwar%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20depending%20on%20defectors%20in%20its%20allotment%20of%20tickets%20wherever%20the%20party%20is%20not%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20it%20looked%20for%20outsiders%20in%20constituencies%20like%20Secunderabad%20and%20Malkajgiri%20within%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%E2%80%99s%20limits%2C%20where%20the%20party%20fared%20badly%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20It%20did%20not%20have%20a%20uniform%20policy%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20adopted%20a%20different%20strategy%20of%20identifying%20strong%20candidates%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20winnability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20state%20general%20secretary%20G.%20Premender%20Reddy%20said%20the%20party%20had%20plenty%20of%20candidates%20to%20choose%20from%20but%20looked%20for%20outsiders%20with%20winning%20chances%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20various%20equations%20and%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Congress%20committee%20working%20president%20B.%20Mahesh%20Kumar%20Goud%20recalled%20that%20one%20of%20the%20three%20BRS%20leaders%20who%20were%20given%20tickets%2C%20Nagender%2C%20was%20a%20former%20Congressman%20who%20jumped%20to%20the%20BRS%20after%20Telangana%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20won%20as%20a%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20candidate%20from%20the%20Asifnagar%20assembly%20constituency%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20united%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20after%20the%20Congress%20denied%20him%20a%20ticket%20during%20the%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Y.S.%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%2C%20but%20resigned%20as%20MLA%20within%20days%20to%20return%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20lost%20the%20following%20by-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20health%20minister%20in%20the%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20next%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBRS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20president%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20on%20Friday%20(March%2022)%20announced%20former%20IPS%20officer%20R.S.%20Praveen%20Kumar%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20from%20Nagarkurnool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Praveen%20Kumar%20resigned%20as%20the%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20to%20join%20the%20BRS%20recently.%20He%20had%20even%20negotiated%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20BSP%20along%20with%20BSP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Ramji%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20day%20later%2C%20Kumar%20announced%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BSP%2C%20saying%20party%20supremo%20Mayawati%20had%20mounted%20pressure%20on%20him%20to%20call%20off%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20contemplated%20the%20allotment%20of%20Nagarkurnool%20and%20Hyderabad%20seats%20to%20the%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20also%20announced%20the%20candidature%20of%20former%20IAS%20officer%20and%20now%20MLC%20P.%20Venkatarami%20Reddy%20from%20the%20Medak%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711119638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22200254%2FSMR-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fp