amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1711162272330000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1N-q5IvkGgog5Mr9UQcvpi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20intra-government%20recruitment%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Secretariat%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20a%20%E2%80%98Senior%20Field%20Officer%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20senior%20position%20within%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20external%20intelligence%20agency%20which%20functions%20within%20the%20Cabinet%20Secretariat.%20The%20CabSec%E2%80%99s%20requirements%20note%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuitable%2Feligible%20officers%E2%80%9D%20should%20%E2%80%9Chave%20keen%20interest%20in%20security%20issues%20and%20international%20affairs%20especially%20in%20the%20field%20of%20gathering%20intelligence%20and%20security%20management%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssuming%20the%2C%20US%20government%20did%20its%20homework%20before%20unsealing%20its%20indictment%2C%20this%20means%20CC1%20was%20a%20senior%20operative%20of%20the%20R%26amp%3BAW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssuming%20he%20had%20gone%20rogue%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20he%20had%20to%20have%20been%20part%20of%20a%20band%20of%20rogue%20operatives%20since%20he%20shared%20footage%20of%20the%20bullet-ridden%20corpse%20of%20another%20Khalistan%20activist%2C%20Hardeep%20Nijjar%2C%20that%20had%20been%20taken%20(presumably%20by%20the%20assassins)%20right%20after%20he%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20on%20June%2018%2C%202023.%20Since%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2