nt%20internal%20investigation%2C%20the%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20ought%20to%20have%20rung%20alarm%20bells.%20Doval%20would%20have%20asked%20Samant%20Goel%20if%20these%20hits%20were%20being%20done%20%E2%80%9Cby%20one%20of%20ours%E2%80%9D.%20And%20if%20the%20answer%20was%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99%20then%20anyone%20tasked%20with%20safeguarding%20national%20security%20would%20surely%20want%20to%20find%20out%20who%20was%20behind%20these%20plots%20since%20the%20list%20of%20potential%20culprits%20might%20include%20a%20hostile%20foreign%20agency%20out%20to%20create%20a%20%E2%80%98false%20flag%E2%80%99%20debacle%20for%20%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20However%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fbc0271e5-c5e4-487f-b130-81fa036f58dc%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fbc0271e5-c5e4-487f-b130-81fa036f58dc%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1711162272330000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2ho4kZNX87hsYze2_EzI6b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0set%20up%20its%20probe%20only%20at%20the%20end%20of%20November%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20than%20three%20months%20after%20the%20US%20first%20shared%20its%20concerns%20on%20the%20Pannun%20case%20with%20Doval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20such%20a%20probe%20been%20ordered%20and%20conducted%20vigorously%20in%20June%2C%20after%20Nijjar%20was%20killed%2C%20or%20in%20August%2C%20the%20rogue%20elements%20would%20have%20been%20identified%20and%20the%20country%20spared%20the%20sort%20of%20diplomatic%20embarrassment%20it%20is%20now%20being%20forced%20to%20deal%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98rogue%E2%80%99%20theory%2C%20then%2C%20is%20this%3A%20The%20fact%20that%20rogue%20operatives%20can%20pull%20