mer-free-electricity-biogas-plant-woman-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeasibility%20of%20urban%20biogas%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20founded%20Greeneria%20in%202014%20to%20champion%20this%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Biogas%20Association%20(IBA)%2C%20which%20is%20instrumental%20in%20forming%20various%20policies%20along%20with%20ministries%20like%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20(MNRE)%2C%20Petroleum%20Ministry%2C%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Water%20and%20Sanitation.%20The%20association%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20initiating%20the%20SATAT%20programme%20and%20the%20GOBARdhan%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%E2%80%99s%20projects%2C%20equipped%20with%20IoT%20technology%2C%20are%20spread%20across%20India%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20and%20major%20IT%20companies%20like%20Hewlett%20Packard%20and%20Capgemini%20to%20shopping%20malls%20like%20Forum%20and%20residential%20complexes.%20Greeneria%20proudly%20shares%20that%20they%20hold%20the%20record%20for%20the%20largest%20residential%20biogas%20system%20in%20India%2C%20providing%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20to%20Prestige%20Jindal%20City%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202262px)%20100vw%2C%202262px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222262%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%202262w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-768x576.jpg%20