estyle-holi-organic-colours-make-at-home-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducing%20Holi%20colours%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20the%20tribe%20and%20selling%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20concept%20of%20natural%20colours%20was%20gaining%20traction%20at%20the%20time.%20We%20first%20launched%20the%20Holi%20colours%20in%202018%20and%20have%20been%20receiving%20more%20orders%20ever%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313885%2Fhyderabad-manya-cherabuddi-makes-natural-dyes-conducts-workshops-sustainable-living%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20colour-making%20process%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaurang%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20colours%20are%20entirely%20natural%20and%20made%20from%20edible%20materials.%20The%20base%20is%20maize%20flour%20cultivated%20by%20the%20community%20itself.%20The%20orange%20colour%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20Palash%20flower%2C%20abundant%20in%20the%20area%20during%20March%20and%20April.%20Our%20yellow%20hue%20combines%20Palash%20flowers%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20turmeric.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%20hues%20are%20concocted%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20various%20forest%20leaves.%20%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20we%20have%20a%20pink%20shade%20crafted%20using%20Ganganagri%20Rose%20along%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20dried%20beetroot%2C%20which%20enhances%20the%20vibrancy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flowers%20are%20first%20picked%2C%20sorted%20and%20cleaned.%20The%20ingredients%20are%20boiled%20for%2014-15%20minutes%20and%20then%20they%20are%20sieved%20to%20segregate%20the%20residue.%20Once%20this%20is%20done%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20dried%20and%20then%20hand-pounded.%20This%20is%20then%20added%20to%20the%20organic%20maize%20flour%20to%20make%20natural%20colours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20primarily%20serves%20customers%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20a%20few%20others%20fr