on%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224000%2B%20People%20Are%20Getting%20Life-Saving%20Dialysis%20Through%20This%20Amazing%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakala%20Devi%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%20from%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Chamoli%20district%2C%20started%20experiencing%20severe%20body%20pain%2C%20fever%2C%20chills%2C%20nausea%2C%20and%20difficulty%20walking%20in%20late%202021.%20During%20the%20course%20of%20her%20work%20in%20her%20district%2C%20these%20symptoms%20caused%20her%20considerable%20discomfort%20and%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20continue%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20visited%20nearby%20doctors%20and%20PHCs%2C%20who%20ordered%20some%20basic%20tests%20and%20prescribed%20medicines.%20After%20two%20weeks%20of%20rest%20at%20home%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20did%20not%20experience%20any%20improvement.%20A%20doctor%20advised%20her%20to%20visit%20a%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%20for%20better%20access%20to%20treatment%2C%20which%20involved%20travelling%20almost%20four%20hours%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%20over%20150%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Government-aided%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20Chandrakala%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F140950%2Findian-scientists-develop-sensor-for-early-detection-of-chronic-kidney-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20kidney%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20advised%20dialysis%20twice%20a%20week.%20As%20this%20treatment%20was%20not%20available%20near%20her%20residence%2C%20she%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20Dehradun%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20two%20nights%20every%20week%20to%20get%20the%20dialysis%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20single%20mother%2C%20being%20separated%20from%20her%20son%2C%20spending%20on%20travel%2C%20and%20eight%20nights%20at%20lodging%20every%20month%2C%20was%20much%20more%20than%20what%20she%20could%20afford%2C%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20faced%20by%20the%20ASHA%20worker%20resonates%20with%20many%20residing%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobal%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20(GBD)%202015%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chronic%20Kidney%20Disease%20(CKD)%20ranks%20as%20the%20eighth%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20India%2C%20largely%20because%20many%20patients%20develop%20complications%20leading%20to%20end-stage%20renal%20disease.%20A%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20two%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20develop%20end-stage%20renal%20disease%20every%20year%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20long-term%20dialysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20costs%20associated%20with%20dialysis%20care%20add%20to%20the%20financial%20woes%20of%20patients.%20Collaborating%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Government%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20identified%20renal%20care%20as%20a%20major%20gap.%20Noticing%20that%20many%20residents%20in%20hilly%20areas%20were%20forced%20to%20migrate%20to%20Dehradun%20or%20Haldwani%20for%20dialysis%2C%20the%20organisation%20decided%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%20by%20establishing%20last-mile%20availability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20throughout%20the%20state%2C%20through%20the%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20a%20single%20centre%20in%20March%202022%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20over%2027%20centres%20across%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Punjab.%20Over%20the%20past%20t